{"tid":1683230,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"龍門冰室又被裝修","createTime":"2019-10-30T14:14:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T14:43:09.000Z","uid":184679,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8b72de4505f973b5e32f78be43f4191937398708","tid":1683230,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T14:14:48.000Z","msg":"大批示威者晚上在警察屯門行動基地外聚集，有人拆除行人路鐵欄、工程膠欄堵塞馬路，有人高叫抗議口號。<br />\n<br />\n晚上近9時半，有黑衣蒙面示威者破壞圍板，闖入前日被縱火破壞的富臨集團旗下「龍門冰室」，大肆搗亂，有人打爛玻璃，有人打爛桌椅，有人將行人路鐵欄丟入餐廳。防暴警察趕到驅散，大批示威者慌忙逃跑。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，「龍門冰室」名稱鬧雙胞胎，其中屯門海麗同香港仔龍門分店，屬富臨集團旗下。與紅磡表明支持示威的「龍門冰室」並不相屬。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">http://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1625505/即時-港聞-修例風波-屯門示威者闖富臨旗下-龍門冰室-搗亂-警察驅散</code></pre>"},{"pid":"bd0dc091c7e63318a55af7c8b547c088b6f50056","tid":1683230,"uid":45255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T14:16:03.000Z","msg":"又嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83832c266f7bb9aafa56f673c613951bff9c81be","tid":1683230,"uid":85965,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T14:17:56.000Z","msg":"Good job"},{"pid":"32cf476c3e6b020eaeceb003c28e4df0671fe78f","tid":1683230,"uid":69899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T14:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d70f4bfc5cf5660e138fda49ab02ff59eeb1a669","tid":1683230,"uid":85604,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T14:19:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n拉30~50個手足換呢間垃圾裝修?<br />\n大家咪鬼再圍狗屋啦好冇呀"},{"pid":"fef3ce5153d9227e34a61f85aae41b27e98bd544","tid":1683230,"uid":92448,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d70f4bfc5cf5660e138fda49ab02ff59eeb1a669","tid":1683230,"uid":85604,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T14:19:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母<br />\n拉30~50個手足換呢間垃圾裝修?<br />\n大家咪鬼再圍狗屋啦好冇呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T14:20:58.000Z","msg":"人各有志, 大家行唔同嘅路, 只要終